text: Kampong Cham Football Club (Khmer: ក្លឹបបាល់ទាត់ខេត្តកំពង់ចាម), is a football club based in Kampong Cham Province, Cambodia. The club was invited by the FFC to compete in the 2019 Cambodian League, the top division of Cambodian football. == Current squad == (Captain) ==References== == External links == Category:Football clubs in Cambodia Category:Sport in Phnom Penh
title: Kampong Cham FC
